Class BucketSource

    public class BucketSource
extends Object
implements StreamingOperation<String>
    Wraps the stream of keys from BucketResponse.getBucketInfo.getKeys in an iterator, handles closing the underlying http stream when finished.

      • BucketSource

        public BucketSource(ListBucketsResponse listBucketsResponse)
        Create a Key Source from an http.ListBucketsResponse in response to {@link RiakClient#listBuckets(boolean) request. The bucket response contains a stream which you must close if you do not iterate over the entire set.
        Parameters:
        listBucketsResponse - the ListBucketsResponse with a List of buckets.
